    <abstract>
      <p>To streamline the analysis and visualization of bacterial growth and gene expression data obtained by microtitre plate readers, we developed BactEXTRACT, an intuitive, easy-to-use R Shiny application. BactEXTRACT simplifies the transition from raw optical density, fluorescence and luminescence measurements to publication-ready plots. This package offers a user-friendly interface that reduces the complexity involved in growth curve and gene expression analysis and is generally applicable. BactEXTRACT is available at <ext-link xlink:href="https://veeninglab.com/bactextract" ext-link-type="uri">https://veeninglab.com/bactextract</ext-link>.</p>
    </abstract>
